name: Buisness Finding
query:
select 
      `tabDaily Report`.engineer_name as "Engineer Name:data/Daily Report:125",
      `tabDaily Report`.working_place as "Location:data/Daily Report:100", 
      `tabLead Details`.doctors_name as "Doctors Name:data/Lead Details:150" ,
      `tabLead Details`.hospital_name as "Hospital Name:data/Lead Details:150" ,
      `tabLead Details`.contact_no as "Contact:data/Lead Details:150" ,
      `tabLead Details`.product_name as "Product:data/Lead Details:150" ,
       `tabLead Details`.special_comment as "Comment:data/Lead Details:200" ,
      `tabDaily Report`.Date as "Date:data/Daily Report:150" 
from `tabDaily Report`,`tabLead Details`
where
     `tabDaily Report`.name=`tabLead Details`.parent
